Glacial Impact.description:
|cff3399ffRequires Frozen Target|r
Call down icy boulders onto a |cff3399ffFrozen|r enemy, dealing 209 Frost damage.

@ext:Damage scales with your critical strike rating. :ext@

Glacial Ward.description:
Activate a |cffffffffGlacial Ward|r on yourself and your Undead minions for 30 min.

While active, maximum Runic Power and Intellect is increased by 10% and the duration of stun effects on you is reduced by 20%.

@ext:Only 1 |cffffffffWard|r can be active at a time.:ext@

Plague of Undeath.description:
Disease an enemy dealing 63 Plague damage every 2.50 sec and reduces the targets Holy healing received by 50% for 20 sec.

If |cffffffffPlague of Undeath|r is dispelled, the enemy takes 231 Plague damage and is stunned for 5 sec.

@ext:Periodic damage dealt by this benefits from your spell haste.:ext@
